# Trocado / Cordato — Expenses
# uv run poe serve   →   uvicorn em 127.0.0.1:8000, hot-reload
# Swagger UI: http://127.0.0.1:8000/schema/swagger
#
# Obtenha um token via http/authentication.http e cole em @token abaixo.
# Após registrar uma despesa, copie o `id` da resposta e cole em @expense_id.

@host = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@token = <paste-token-here>
@expense_id = <paste-expense-id-here>

### Registrar despesa → 201 Created
POST {{host}}/v1/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "49.90",
  "occurred_on": "2026-06-28",
  "description": "almoço"
}

### Registrar despesa sem descrição (campo opcional) → 201 Created
POST {{host}}/v1/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "15.00",
  "occurred_on": "2026-06-29"
}

### Registrar despesa com valor inválido → 422 Unprocessable Entity
POST {{host}}/v1/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "0",
  "occurred_on": "2026-06-28"
}

### Listar despesas vivas (mais recente primeiro) → 200 OK
GET {{host}}/v1/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Editar despesa (substitui todos os campos) → 200 OK
PATCH {{host}}/v1/expenses/{{expense_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "55.00",
  "occurred_on": "2026-06-29",
  "description": "jantar"
}

### Remover despesa (soft-delete) → 204 No Content
DELETE {{host}}/v1/expenses/{{expense_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Qualquer rota sem autenticação → 401 Unauthorized
GET {{host}}/v1/expenses
